Introduction
Karthik Piano is a virtual piano web application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The application allows users to play piano keys using their keyboard, record and playback their performances, and customize the piano theme and instrument.
Features
Virtual piano keyboard with interactive keys
Record and playback functionality
Settings menu for theme and instrument selection
Social sharing buttons for Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram
Responsive design for various devices
Installation
Clone the repository using git clone https://github.com/your-username/karthik-piano.git
Open the index.html file in a web browser to run the application
Usage
Use your keyboard to play the piano keys
Click the "Record" button to start recording your performance
Click the "Playback" button to listen to your recorded performance
Use the settings menu to select a theme or instrument
